# 🌦️ Weather Warden

Weather Warden is a modern weather forecasting web application built using **React.js** and powered by the **OpenWeatherMap API**. It provides real-time weather updates and a 5-day forecast for any city worldwide.

## 🔧 Features

- Real-time weather updates
- 5-day forecast with icons
- Search any global city
- Responsive design (desktop/mobile)
- Error handling for invalid cities

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- React.js
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- OpenWeatherMap API
- Axios
- CSS3
- Vite (build tool)

## 📦 Installation

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
